name: "san la ricarda"
description:
Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.
we have news of him! Ricardus was missing for several days but it's normal for him, he got angry for not being able to find the perfect costume for halloween and decided to take a trip to tijuana to celebrate the day of the dead.
lucky you are back my friend!
